txt.en: Thunash can be found at Cotfast in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should summon and confront Thunash.
You have defeated Thunash and assisted the Free Peoples of the Wildwood.
A bounty notice asks you to seek out Thunash, a wicked half-orc in Wildwood.
'Oh Sharkey will hear about this. Mark my words!'

The bounty notice reads:

'Have you heard of the emissary of Sharkey, striding through the Wildwood like he owns the place? To this I refute, not if we have anything to say about it!

'Thunash the half-orc believes the Wildwood is his to burn and conquer. A reward to any who can bring this vile half-orc down.'
